# Job Application Management System

# Overview
    The Job Application Management System is a web-based application designed to streamline the process of job applications. It allows users to submit their application details, view submitted applications, and bookmark specific jobs for easy reference.

# Features
    Form Submission: Users can fill out a form to submit their job application details including Name, Email, Role, and Expected Salary.

    Data Storage: Application data is stored locally using Local Storage.

    Dynamic Data Display: Submitted applications are displayed dynamically in a structured table format.

    Sorting and Filtering: Users can sort applications by Name and Salary, and filter by Role.

    Bookmarking: Users can bookmark specific job applications for easy access.

# Technologies Used
    Front-end: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

    Storage: Local Storage

